Git is the single source of truth for everything; 

	1. Application code 
	2. Infrastructure code
	3. Kubernetes Manifests 
	4. Ci/CD pipeline definitions. 

Real - world Example: 
	
	A bank using AWS AWS + Azure -- stores all microservices and terraform modules in Github Enterprise. 
	
	Every change --> pull request (PR request) --> review --> Merge --> Pipeline triggers. 
